# Mobile Sales Dashboard - Power BI 📱📊

This Power BI dashboard provides insights into mobile phone sales across cities in India. It visualizes sales performance, payment methods, customer ratings, and daily trends to help business teams track product performance and sales metrics.

## 🔍 Dashboard Highlights

- 📍 **Total Sales & Quantity** KPIs
- 🗺️ **Sales by City** (Map visual)
- 📆 **Sales Trend by Day**
- 🛍️ **Transactions by Payment Method** (Pie chart)
- ⭐ **Customer Ratings Distribution**
- 📱 **Sales by Mobile Model** (Bar chart)
- 📊 **Sales by Weekday**
- 🧮 Interactive filters: Month, Brand, Day Name, Mobile Model, and Payment Method

## 🛠️ Tools & Skills

- Power BI Desktop
- Power Query (Data Cleaning)
- DAX (KPIs and measures)
- Visual storytelling and slicers

